data.description: Welcome to a rare find in the heart of Seminole. This 4 bedroom, 2 bath home has been beautifully renovated and is ready for your perfect home. You are located on a quiet street in a no-flood zone, on a large lot just 15 minutes from the beaches. Upon entry, you are greeted with a large open floor plan with natural light pouring in. The kitchen opens up to the dining area and features granite countertops, a new backsplash, and stainless steel appliances. There is a HUGE separate bonus living room conveniently located off the dining area. There are (3) bedrooms, (1) bathroom downstairs, and an indoor utility/laundry room. Upstairs, you walk into the master bedroom, a TRUE retreat with vaulted ceilings, a large walk-in closet, and an ensuite bathroom. The large backyard is a blank canvas ready for you to make it your own. Plans for your entertaining outdoor kitchen are included and can be wrapped up into mortgage. Roof (2018), HVAC (2016), Plumbing & Electrical updated within the last 5 years. The property has its own dog kennel. If you have been looking for a turnkey property in a quiet area, this is it! Call today for your private showing. $1500 bonus with acceptance date before 11/22/2023.
